author: Laura Meckler
title: Senate Immigration Debate Proceeds at a ‘Glacial’ Pace
text:
WASHINGTON—Senators promised an open-ended, free-wheeling immigration debate, where nobody knows what will happen. On Day Two, what happened wasn’t a lot.
There were brief speeches and positioning by both sides, but no votes.
